summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2951, for the improvement of Rainier Avenue, from Kenny Street to Thistle Street, all in the City of Seattle, by planking the westerly side thereof, under Ordinance No. 35606 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
